These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, december, march, april, may, february, january
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, british, chinese, dutch, egyptian, french, german
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: scientific, western, animation, zombie, family, adventure, spy
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, oliveros, cain, vegafina, pall-mall, bongani, bolivar
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching family movies is the dutch##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the british is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the german##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the vegafina-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the french##2
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is the swisher-smoker##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the french is the cain-smoker##1
15. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the german##1
16. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
17. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the chinese##1
18. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the egyptian##1
19. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Birthday      | december  | february        | may | march      | april     | june      | january     |
| Nationality   | british | dutch         | german   | australian | french    | egyptian | chinese |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | family | scientific | western | spy  | adventure  | zombie    |
| Cigar     | pall-mall  | bongani         | swisher     | oliveros    | cain | vegafina     | bolivar     |

